para_trans: Kalyan to Shil, which is part of the Bhiwandi-Kalyan-Shilphata road.
Government Decision No. Khakesh-2023 / Q. No.262 / Roads-8
Bhiwandi-Kalyan-Shilphata at the meeting of the Hon'ble Cabinet dated 25.02.2024
The road from Kalyan to Shil, which forms part of the road, is called "V.H.B.P. Sri Sant Savlaram Maharaj Mhatre."
Kalyan to Shil, which is part of the Bhiwandi-Kalyan-Shilphata road.
Naming of "VHP Shri Sant Savlaram Maharaj Mhatre" is being approved.
The decision was taken by the Government of Maharashtra.
